Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 2. | Description :The Borrower shall prepare and furnish to the Bank interimunaudited financial reports for the Project covering the quarter. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 3. | Description :Audited Financial Statements shall be in accordance with theprovisions of Section 5.09 (b), GC, and shall be furnished to the Banknot later than six months after the end of such period. |Frequency :Yearly
